<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 12:20:33 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>俄罗斯城市被洪水淹没的动物收容所称“我们就像诺亚方舟”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/were-like-noahs-ark-says-animal-shelter-flooded-russian-city-2024-04-12/</link><description>周五，遭受洪水袭击的俄罗斯奥伦堡市荒凉的街道上充满了水泵的轰鸣声，人们争先恐后地听从官方的逃生警告。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 12:12:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/were-like-noahs-ark-says-animal-shelter-flooded-russian-city-2024-04-12/</guid></item><item><title>Valieva 的鸡尾酒药物引起了人们对补充剂危险的担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/valievas-cocktail-medicines-raises-concerns-around-supplement-dangers-2024-04-12/</link><description>俄罗斯青少年花样滑冰运动员卡米拉·瓦利耶娃（Kamila Valieva）被禁止服用 56 种药物和膳食辅助品的消息曝光，让人们认识到合法补充剂的黑暗世界，受污染的粉末或措辞不当的标签可能会给一名精英运动员带来灾难。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 11:15:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/valievas-cocktail-medicines-raises-concerns-around-supplement-dangers-2024-04-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国加强股票市场交易、上市监管</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-strengthens-stock-market-trading-listing-regulations-2024-04-12/</link><description>中国证券监管机构周五发布了加强公司上市、退市和量化交易监管的规则草案，以改善股票市场，保护投资者利益。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 11:04:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-strengthens-stock-market-trading-listing-regulations-2024-04-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车品牌Hyper表示将于2026年在其汽车中使用全固态电池</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-brand-hyper-says-will-use-all-solid-state-batteries-its-cars-2026-2024-04-12/</link><description>中国电动汽车制造商广汽艾安旗下Hyper品牌周五表示，已完成全固态电池的研发，将​​于2026年首次应用于Hyper汽车。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 10:36:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-brand-hyper-says-will-use-all-solid-state-batteries-its-cars-2026-2024-04-12/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯城市因洪水上涨呼吁大规模疏散</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russian-city-calls-mass-evacuation-due-rising-flood-waters-2024-04-12/</link><description>周五，俄罗斯城市奥伦堡当局呼吁居民立即撤离，原因是主要河流因积雪融化而决堤，洪水迅速上涨。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 10:17:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russian-city-calls-mass-evacuation-due-rising-flood-waters-2024-04-12/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：目光转向盈利、中国贸易失误、中东紧张局势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-04-12/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 10:05:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-04-12/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，由于兄弟的监管职责，顶级银行家退出中金公司</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/top-banker-exiting-cicc-china-sovereign-fund-due-brothers-regulator-role-sources-2024-04-12/</link><description>六位消息人士称，离开投资银行中国国际金融公司（中金公司）的一名高管将加入主权财富基金中投公司，以避免与他的兄弟担任证券监管机构主管时发生潜在的利益冲突。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 08:50:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/top-banker-exiting-cicc-china-sovereign-fund-due-brothers-regulator-role-sources-2024-04-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国3月铁矿石进口量小幅增长，​​钢材出口量创8年新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-march-iron-ore-imports-edge-up-steel-exports-near-8-year-high-2024-04-12/</link><description>周五海关数据显示，中国3月份铁矿石进口量同比增长约0.5%，因预计春节假期后需求将回升，因为钢铁制造商通常会提高产量。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 08:41:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-march-iron-ore-imports-edge-up-steel-exports-near-8-year-high-2024-04-12/</guid></item><item><title>来访的中国贸易官员就绿色科技调查向欧盟发出警告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-puzzled-by-eu-probes-evs-solar-panels-wind-turbines-minister-says-2024-04-12/</link><description>中国最高贸易官员周五警告布鲁塞尔反对保护主义，称北京对欧盟对绿色技术出口的调查以及欧盟担心它们威胁国内太阳能电池板、风力涡轮机和电动汽车行业感到困惑。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 08:36:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-puzzled-by-eu-probes-evs-solar-panels-wind-turbines-minister-says-2024-04-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国因负面言论召见日本、菲律宾外交官</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-summons-japanese-diplomat-over-negative-comments-summit-2024-04-12/</link><description>中国外交部表示，中方周五召见日本和菲律宾外交官，对美日菲领导人峰会期间发表的负面言论表示不满。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 08:25:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-summons-japanese-diplomat-over-negative-comments-summit-2024-04-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国最大贸易展上的关键词是“低价”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/low-price-is-word-chinas-largest-trade-show-2024-04-12/</link><description>从周一开始，外国买家将涌入中国最大的贸易博览会的广阔大厅，寻找中国商品的交易，美国和欧洲政府抱怨这些商品正在涌入全球市场。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 08:19:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/low-price-is-word-chinas-largest-trade-show-2024-04-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国军队愿与越南提升战略互信水平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-military-willing-raise-strategic-trust-level-with-vietnam-2024-04-12/</link><description>中国国防部长周五在一份声明中表示，中国国防部长向越南国防部长表示，中国愿意将两军战略互信提升到新水平。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 08:12:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-military-willing-raise-strategic-trust-level-with-vietnam-2024-04-12/</guid></item><item><title>德国官员称，肖尔茨将在中国之行中提出俄罗斯产能过剩问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/scholz-will-raise-russia-overcapacity-china-trip-german-officials-say-2024-04-12/</link><description>德国官员周五表示，德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨将在访华期间对中国对俄罗斯的支持以及中国产能过剩问题提出担忧。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 07:54:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/scholz-will-raise-russia-overcapacity-china-trip-german-officials-say-2024-04-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国3月进出口萎缩 大幅低于预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-march-exports-imports-shrink-miss-forecasts-by-big-margins-2024-04-12/</link><description>中国3月份出口大幅萎缩，进口意外萎缩，大幅低于预期，突显政策制定者在试图支撑摇摇欲坠的经济复苏时面临的艰巨任务。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 07:43:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-march-exports-imports-shrink-miss-forecasts-by-big-margins-2024-04-12/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯媒体称，中国收紧俄罗斯付款审查，打击电子元件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-tightens-russia-payments-scrutiny-hitting-electronics-components-say-2024-04-12/</link><description>俄罗斯两家新闻媒体周五报道称，俄罗斯公司在向中国付款时面临越来越多的障碍，其中一家称涉及电子零部件的交易受到了影响。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 07:24:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-tightens-russia-payments-scrutiny-hitting-electronics-components-say-2024-04-12/</guid></item></channel></rss>